      "num": 5,
      "text": "In civil litigation, an attorney challenges the admissibility of testimony from a forensic accountant under the Daubert Standard. Which factor would the court be LEAST likely to consider?",
      "tag": "Daubert Standard",
      "options": [
        "A. Whether the theory or technique can be tested and has been tested",
        "B. Whether the method has been peer-reviewed and published",
