    {
      "num": 7,
      "text": "A CFE is retained as an expert witness in a wire fraud prosecution. Under Federal Rules of Evidence 702, what is the examiner's primary obligation before providing opinion testimony?",
      "tag": "Expert Witness Qualification and Daubert Standards",
      "options": [
        "D. Testify only regarding investigative procedures, explicitly avoiding conclusions about fraud elements",
        "A. Demonstrate specialized knowledge, training, and experience that will reliably assist the trier of fact using sound methodologies",
