      ],
      "correct": 1,
      "justification_correct": "FRE 702 (as clarified by Daubert v. Merrell Dow Pharmaceuticals) requires expert testimony be based on reliable principles, proper application, and specialized knowledge assisting the factfinder. CFE qualifications, methodology, and relevance satisfy this standard.",
      "justification_wrong": "FRE 702 does not require prosecutor certification, does not exclude interpretive opinions, and does not prohibit conclusions about fraud elements. Expert may testify on methodology, findings, and reasonable conclusions within expert scope.",
